snippet.title: STARSEEKER: Astroneer Expeditions - Game Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1454370/STARSEEKER_Astroneer_Expeditions/
SIGN UP TO HEAR FIRST ABOUT BETA ACCESS: https://bit.ly/strskrbeta

We are excited to announce the next game from System Era, STARSEEKER: Astroneer Expeditions. STARSEEKER is a new game set within the Astroneer universe with a focus on discovery, cooperative expeditions, and camaraderie. Exploring deep space on the ESS Starseeker, players will need to work together with the entire crew of the space station to complete planet- wide objectives across a multitude of star systems using cutting edge technology. Coming in 2026.
